        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter in regard to the bank card issue. I collected a letter without a card in it. This could be in the wrong hands.",
        "On August 15, I received a package from your bank. On opening, I found only a bank statement for the last year. Again today, I got another letter from the bank asking me to acknowledge for getting a new bank card which I never received. I am alarmed at the situation as either the card got lost or was stolen. Either way, this can negatively affect me.",
